---
// Orders.astro - Componente para gestión de pedidos
---

<div class="orders-container">
  <div class="orders-header">
    <h2><svg class="icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 3h5v5"/><path d="M8 3H3v5"/><path d="M12 22v-8.3a4 4 0 0 0-1.172-2.872L3 3"/><path d="m15 9 6 6"/><path d="M9 9 3 3"/></svg> Gestión de Pedidos</h2>
    <p>Sistema de pedidos en desarrollo</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="orders-placeholder">
    <div class="placeholder-card">
      <h3><svg class="icon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0H9m12 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg> Próximamente</h3>
      <p>Esta sección incluirá:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Lista de pedidos activos</li>
        <li>Historial de pedidos</li>
        <li>Estados de preparación</li>
        <li>Tiempos de entrega</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .orders-container {
    padding: 24px;
    background: #f7f6f3;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
  }
  .orders-header {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .orders-header h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #37352f;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .orders-header p {
    color: #787774;
  }
  .placeholder-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid #e9e9e7;
  }
  .placeholder-card h3 {
    color: #37352f;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .placeholder-card ul {
    margin-left: 20px;
    color: #787774;
  }
</style>